":"比大陸乞丐 =&gt; $500, 香港清潔工 =&gt; 一粒朱古力<br />\n<br />\n當中隱含啲咩, 自己慢慢參透<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1651f03aee502168564e5cd9e69070eb6369bb17","tid":579264,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T06:12:28.000Z","msg":"難在派錢都可以攪到PAT屎咁"}]}